OL,3,CPay jumps 55% for P&O boss as ferry
OL,4,Ccompany posts loss of #91 million
OL,6,FThe earnings of the boss of P&O
OL,7,FFerries soared in 2023, a year in
OL,8,Fwhich the company continued to be
OL,9,Fheavily loss-making.
OL,11,FThe much-delayed annual accounts have
OL,12,Fbeen filed to Companies House and will
OL,13,Fsoon be published, but have been seen
OL,14,Fby ITV News and the Guardian.
OL,16,FThe accounts show that P&O lost #91.4
OL,17,Fmillion before tax during 2023, down
OL,18,Ffrom #246 million the year before.
