OL,6,FPeter Hebblethwaite, the chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, was paid #683,000 -
OL,8,Frepresenting an increase of at least
OL,9,F55% on the earnings of P&O's highest-
OL,10,Fpaid director in 2022.
OL,12,FThe rise in Hebblethwaite's pay is
OL,13,Flikely to fuel renewed anger, coming
OL,14,Fjust a year after P&O sacked 786 crew
OL,15,Fwithout notice and replaced them with
OL,16,Fcheaper agency workers paid as little
OL,17,Fas #4.87 an hour.
