OL,6,FThe financial accounts of P&O Ferries
OL,7,FDivision Holdings Limited show
OL,8,FHebblethwaite's earnings were higher
OL,9,Fthan the amounts he disclosed to MPs
OL,10,Flast May.
OL,12,FHebblethwaite told the Business and
OL,13,FTrade parliamentary select committee
OL,14,Fthat he earned a #325,000 salary, plus
OL,15,Fa bonus of #183,000 for 2023.
OL,17,FDuring his appearance, MPs asked if he
OL,18,Fwas "a pirate" who appeared to be
OL,19,F"robbing staff blind".
