OL,6,FHebblethwaite told MPs: "I reflected
OL,7,Fon accepting that (bonus). But
OL,8,Fultimately I did decide to accept it."
OL,10,FHe added: "I do recognise it is not a
OL,11,Fdecision that everyone would have
OL,12,Fmade."
OL,14,FP&O Ferries sacked its mainly British
OL,15,Fcrews in March 2022 in order to cut
OL,16,Fits costs and avoid bankruptcy, but
OL,17,Fthe company still lost money in 2023.
