OL,6,FIn a note, accompanying the accounts,
OL,7,FP&O's directors say the company "has
OL,8,Fbeen on a transformational journey, as
OL,9,Fit has progressed its recovery from
OL,10,Fthe challenges of the global Covid-19
OL,11,Fpandemic, Brexit and the impact of the
OL,12,Fdisruption caused by the change in the
OL,13,Fcrewing model."
OL,15,FThe company carried 4.5 million
OL,16,Fpassengers in 2023, an increase on the
OL,17,Fyear before when its service was
OL,18,Fdisrupted by the sackings and the
OL,19,Fsubsequent detention of some of its
OL,20,Fships by the authorities.
