OL,6,FIn 2019, P&O carried 7.7 million
OL,7,Fpassengers.
OL,9,FFreight volumes also remain well below
OL,10,Fpre-pandemic levels. The accounts
OL,11,Fstate that P&O "is not seeing the
OL,12,F(freight) market growth it had
OL,13,Fpreviously predicted" and says
OL,14,F"recessionary pressures" are in part
OL,15,Fto blame.
OL,17,FIn adversity, P&O Ferries continues to
OL,18,Frely on its owner, DP World, to stay
OL,19,Fin business.
