OL,6,FDP World - a company from Dubai that
OL,7,Fruns ports and shipping terminals
OL,8,Faround the world - has provided a
OL,9,Fletter of support, indicating a
OL,10,Fwillingness to continue to fund P&O's
OL,11,Flosses.
OL,13,FP&O is not currently repaying interest
OL,14,Fon a #295 million loan from DP World -
OL,15,Finstead the debt is accumulating. And
OL,16,Fthere has been a sharp increase of
OL,17,Flease liabilities to #241 million in
OL,18,F2023, compared with #14.5 million the
OL,19,Fprevious year.
