OL,6,FP&O's accounts are nine months late,
OL,7,Fprompting MPs to question the
OL,8,Fcompany's viability, and are signed
OL,9,Foff by Just Audit & Assurance - a tiny
OL,10,Ffour-person audit-firm that replaced
OL,11,FKPMG, the accounting giant that
OL,12,Fresigned in March.
OL,14,FThe accounts were already overdue when
OL,15,FJust Audit & Assurance were appointed.
