OL,6,F"These delayed accounts are still
OL,7,Fincomplete. They also suggest P&O
OL,8,FFerries is in deep financial trouble,"
OL,9,Fsaid Professor Atul Shah of City
OL,10,FUniversity.
OL,12,FHe added: "As a Limited Liability
OL,13,Fcompany which is of significant public
OL,14,Finterest to Britain, P&O Ferries can
OL,15,Fonly continue trading because DP World
OL,16,Fis willing to underwrite its still
OL,17,Fconsiderable losses. That is a highly
OL,18,Fprecarious situation to be in for most
OL,19,Fstakeholders."
