OL,6,FDespite ongoing losses, P&O maintains
OL,7,Fthat it is on a path to recovery, but
OL,8,Fits wage bill will have risen
OL,9,Fsignificantly in 2024.
OL,11,FA change in the law in France and the
OL,12,FUK now compels all ferry operators to
OL,13,Fpay the minimum wage to crews on the
OL,14,Fcross-channel routes.
OL,16,FIn its accounts, P&O says, "We are
OL,17,Funequivocally committed to adhering to
OL,18,Fthe legal requirements of applicable
OL,19,Fnational and international laws."
